### 2.2 Example Output Comparison

**Without BPL:**

```typescript
// LLM generates without context
class UserService {
  constructor(private http: HttpClient) {}

  createUser(data: any) {
    return this.http.post('/users', data);
  }

  validateUser(data: any) {
    if (!data.email) throw new Error('Email required');
