    ## NAMING CONVENTIONS (PEP 8)

    ### Variables, Functions, Methods
    - Use lowercase with underscores: `user_name`, `calculate_total()`
    - Be descriptive but concise
    - Avoid single letters except for counters (i, j, k) or math contexts

