### 2.3 Compression Strategy for Python Best Practices

**Source:** `docs/PYTHON_BEST_PRACTICES.md` (1384 lines, ~20KB)
**Target:** ~200-400 tokens (~800-1600 characters)

**Compression Approach:**

```
Level 1: MINIMAL (~100 tokens)
