```python
def _deduplicate_interfaces(self, interfaces: List[InterfaceInfo]) -> List[InterfaceInfo]:
    """Remove duplicate interface definitions."""
    seen = {}
    for iface in interfaces:
        key = (iface.name, iface.file_path)
        if key not in seen:
            seen[key] = iface
    return list(seen.values())
```

