Supports tiered output for different use cases:
  - COMPACT: Maximum compression with truncation (~800-2000 tokens)
  - PROMPT: Full context for AI prompts, no truncation on important items
  - FULL: Complete extraction, no truncation anywhere
  - JSON: Machine-readable full export
